name: PassOrRefer
title: Pass Or Refer
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This value set contains concepts that represent findings that indicate the normal findings on hearing examination or referral is needed.),(Data Element Scope: This value set may use the Quality Data Model (QDM) attribute related to Result. The intent of this data element is to identify patients who received a newborn hearing screening with result of pass or refer.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes only relevant concepts associated with SNOMED CT codes representing concepts associated with normal finding on hearing examination and referral.),(Exclusion Criteria: No exclusions.)
